A book is titled: Harmega's rise to power.
Harmega wasn't always as powerful as she
is now. She used to be a powerful wizard
But then one day she decided to persue
immortality and made a deal with a demon.
She then betrayed and overpowered the
demon, and took his lifeforce into her own.
This was the day she became a demi-god.
Harmega is not a god in the traditional
sense. She is still bound to a mortal body.
